@startuml
!includeurl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/proveo-ca/identity/refs/heads/main/proveo.iuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor User

package "Docker Container (Harness: Chess Coach)" {
    
    package "Web UI" {
        [SolidJS Chessboard] as SolidJS
        [Stockfish Web Worker\n(stockfish-18-lite.js)] as StockfishWorker
    }

    package "Ktor Backend Bridge" {
        [Ktor REST API] as Ktor
    }

    [Harness Daemon\n(Kotlin CLI)] as Harness

    package "LLM Layer" {
        [Commentary Agent\n(LlmClient)] as Commentary
    }

    package "Engine Layer" {
        [EngineBridge\n(facade)] as Bridge
        [StockfishEngine] as SFEngine
        [MaiaEngine] as MaiaEng
    }

    package "External Binaries" {
        [Stockfish + Syzygy Tablebases] as Stockfish
        [lc0 + Maia Weights + openings.bin] as Lc0
    }

    database "State Storage" as State {
        [game_state.fen] as FEN
    }
}

package "External Service" {
    [Ollama LLM Server] as Ollama
}

User <---> SolidJS : User Actions / Board render
SolidJS <-> Ktor : HTTP Requests (Move/Advice/Hello/New)
SolidJS <-> StockfishWorker : Local UCI (Hint / Hover Eval)
Ktor ..> State : (Reset only) StateReader for /new

Ktor <--> Harness : JSON-line daemon protocol\n(stdin/stdout)

Harness --> Bridge : Evaluation / Move / Legality
Bridge --> SFEngine : Eval, legality, FEN derivation
Bridge --> MaiaEng : AI move selection
SFEngine --> Stockfish : UCI Protocol
MaiaEng --> Lc0 : UCI Protocol

Harness --> Commentary : Generate coaching advice
Commentary --> Ollama : HTTP (OpenAI-compatible API)

Harness --> State : Writes FEN\n(persistence/debug)

User -[hidden]-> SolidJS

@enduml
